data.eml:eml: A checklist of the centipedes (Chilopoda) of Lithuania

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Tuf, Ivan Hadrián, Ivinskis, Povilas, Rimšaitė, Jolanta (2015): A checklist of the centipedes (Chilopoda) of Lithuania. Zootaxa 4052 (3): 394-400, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4052.3.9
